  "style": "IEEE",
  "texts": [
    "After sorting by samtools, duplicated reads were removed using MarkDuplicates in Picard v1.13 (http:// broad insti tute. github.",
    "io/ picard/).",
    "Average depth was ~27.5× and mapping rate > 90% for each Tartary buckwheat accession.",
    "SNPs and small indels (1-50 bp) were called using the GATK pipeline [65].",
    "Variants were called using GATK HaplotypeCaller, and then a joint-genotyping analysis of the gVCFs was performed on all merged samples."
  ],
